subterm2.pl	  Benchmark on specialization of a modular program
		  with cycles. 

subterm2_1mod.pl  One module version of the benchmark.

To perform the benchmark, do the following steps:

1. start a CiaoPP preprocessor top-level.

2. Type:

   set_pp_flag(local_control,off).
   set_pp_flag(success_policy,botall).
   set_pp_flag(fixpoint,di).
   set_pp_flag(collapse_ai_vers,off).
   use_module(plai(intermod)).

3. Analyze the modular program:

   auto_analyze(shfr, subterm2).

4. Specialize the modular program:

   auto_transform(shfr, spec, subterm2).

The specialized program is generated in the files *_out.pl. 


